Because I love it.

100
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:50,123
<i>"There was once a merchant</i>

101
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:52,885
<i>"in the famous market at Baghdad.</i>

102
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:56,521
<i>"One day he saw a stranger
looking at him in surprise.</i>

103
00:04:56,600 --> 00:05:00,366
<i>"And he knew
that the stranger was Death.</i>

104
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:04,164
<i>"Pale and trembling,
the merchant fled the marketplace</i>

105
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:07,045
<i>"and made his way many, many miles</i>

106
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:09,049
<i>"to the city of Samarra.</i>

107
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:13,402
<i>"For there he was sure Death
