108
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:16,083
<i>"But when, at last, he came to Samarra,</i>

109
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:18,970
<i>"the merchant saw, waiting for him,</i>

110
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,849
<i>"the grim figure of Death.</i>

111
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:25,566
<i>"'Very well,' said the merchant.</i>

112
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:29,130
